com.collabnet.ccf.core.ga
Class GenericArtifactField

java.lang.Object
  com.collabnet.ccf.core.ga.GenericArtifactField

public class GenericArtifactField
extends java.lang.Object

A field has a name and a field type and contains a typed value for the property of the artifact that is described by this field. If a field with the same name and field type occurs more than once, this indicates a multi-value property within the artifact. The content of the field element varies from value type to value type, but it is always encoded as a string, so structured values are currently not allowed.

Author:
jnicolai
